rdinate on storage formats, access patterns, and data retention policies. |
| Bob | Bob's APIs may serve Ivan's model predictions. Coordinate on inference A
PI design, request/response formats, and latency budgets. |
| Eve | ML infrastructure. Training compute, GPU allocation, model serving infra
structure, and CI/CD for model deployments. |
| Heidi | ML security. Adversarial inputs, model poisoning, data privacy (differ
ential privacy, federated learning), and secure model serving. |
