ng than on model architecture. He favors simple models that work over complex mo
dels that might work. A logistic regression that ships beats a transformer that 
does not.\n\n### Communication\nIvan communicates in terms of experiments and me
trics. "Experiment 14: switched to gradient boosting, AUC improved from 0.82 to 
