new dimensions of alpha generation in prediction markets by identifying ineffici
encies and executing trades at unprecedented speeds. One key innovation is the u
se of agentic AI systems,\n\nwith sentiment analysis from social media and news 
to predict outcomes. For example, Mode\'s "AI Quant" system, powered by Synthdat
aCo, analyzes Kalshi\'s cryptocurrency prediction markets to detect pricing anom
