market rebalancing**, **combinatorial arbitrage**, and **cross-platform arbitrag
e**. The most straightforward of these-market rebalancing-occurs when the combin
ed price of "Yes" and "No" shares in a binary market falls below $1.00, guarante
eing a risk-free profit. For instance, if "Yes" is priced at $0.52 and "No" at $
